DEFINITIONS
AND
DATA NOTES
Metro Minnesota includes the seven counties of Anoka, Carver, Dakota, Hennepin, Ramsey, Scott, and Washington in the Twin Cities area.
Greater Minnesota includes the eighty counties outside the seven-county metropolitan area.
Marriage Rate: Number of marriages per 1,000 population.
Divorce Rate: Number of divorces and annulments per 1,000 population.
Data Note: Divorce and Marriage Dissolution are used interchangeably in this newsletter.
Data Note: Marriage dissolutions include annulments for the purposes of this newsletter.
